results.title: Effect of antihypertensives on sexual function and quality of life: the TAIM Study.
results.text_hl: Erection@<m>DISEASE_Alcohol_Related_Disorders</m> @DISEASE_MESH:D019973 @@@-related@@@ problems worsened in 28% (95% CI, 15% to 41%) of @SPECIES_9606 @@@men@@@ receiving @CHEMICAL_Chlorthalidone @CHEMICAL_MESH:D002752 @@@chlorthalidone@@@ and usual diet compared with 3% (CI, 0% to 9%) of those receiving placebo and usual diet (P = 0.009) and 11% (CI, 2% to 20%) of those receiving @<m>CHEMICAL_Atenolol</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001262 @@@atenolol@@@ and usual diet (P greater than 0.05).
